title: MONDAY - Super Wild Card Weekend 2021
itunes:title: MONDAY - Super Wild Card Weekend 2021
description:
It was an exciting Super Wild Card Weekend...the Browns pulling off the upset over the Steelers (0:13). Quarterback Baker Mayfield spoke about the win (0:55) despite all the obstacles. The Ravens took down the Titans (1:33) as Lamar Jackson talks about leaving the field without shaking hands with Titans players (1:57). Drew Brees and the Saints (2:41) advance to a showdown with Tom Brady and the Bucs in a matchup of two future hall of famers(2:59)...and the Packers and Rams prepare to battle in the other NFC Divisional matchup (3:39)
